<item>
            <title>[HIVE-6837] HiveServer2 thrift/http mode &amp; binary mode proxy user check fails reporting IP null for client</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-6837</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hive Server running thrift/http with Kerberos security.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Kinited user knox attempting to proxy as sam.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Beeline connection failed reporting error on hive server logs:&lt;br/&gt;
Caused by: org.apache.hadoop.security.authorize.AuthorizationException: Unauthorized connection for super-user: knox from IP null&lt;/p&gt;</description>
